effects: e1,e2,e3 are nothing but classes

a_count="" a_duration="" a_delay="" a_pause="" a_transform=""
a_animate="[{a1},{a2},,{an}]" a_count="" a_duration="" a_delay="" a_on="" a_pause=""
a_hover="e1", a_hover="{}"
a_toggleClick=""
a_click=""
a_effect="e1,e2,e3,e4" a_on="" 
a_effect="{bounce to right},{spin on path}"
a_effect="{bounce(max,min or fix) to right(max,min or fix)},{spin on path},{break(effect:glass) in last},{when done }"

a_effect="{after 30s easyBounce(300px,20px) to right(min:20px) on click and spin once and ... and break(like glass) in last},{repeat 30 times or upto 10s whichever is low},{do nothing},{restore(original state)}"


to|from				position
before|on|after 	event|time|duration|action
do 					action
upto 				duratoin|count (once,times)
and 				combined effects
or 					
whichever 			condition
low|high 			operators


